                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10143" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2553</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">204 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">桃园之梦：望蕊山庄的农文旅融合创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Peach Blossom Dream: Wangrui’s Innovative Integration of Agriculture, Culture, and Tourism</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鲁莎莎，萨欣怡，李现康，马长江</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顺平县望蕊山庄生态园林有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农文旅融合；地理标志；全产业链；乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">integration of agriculture, culture and tourism; geographical indications; the whole industry chain; rural revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了顺平县望蕊山庄在传统农业模式中走出的一条创新之路。作为扎根山区的民营企业，望蕊山庄最初依托桃花节吸引游客，却因“花期短、果难销”陷入发展瓶颈。面对现实困境，身为“全国劳动模范”的创始人张国桥从“卖桃”转向“卖场景”“卖品牌”，带领团队从零打造合作社、布局电商渠道、引入专家团队推进科技种植，并开发桃酒等深加工产品延伸产业链。当桃子成功贴上地理标志小红标，走进展会平台、各大商超时，望蕊山庄也从一家小农庄蜕变为具备区域品牌力和科技竞争力的产业标杆。一路走来，望蕊山庄并未独享红利，而是通过“桃园+旅游”模式带动17个行政村、712户建档立卡贫困户实现脱贫，张国桥也因此成为河北省“脱贫攻坚奉献奖”获得者。荣耀背后总是挑战重重，现在的望蕊山庄正站在二次跃升的十字路口。未来，它是否能借助智慧农业完成“新破局”？张国桥又将如何带领这片桃林再启传奇？案例展现了望蕊山庄在乡村振兴战略背景下，如何通过差异化战略与全产业链布局突破传统农业发展局限，其“资源整合—技术升级—品牌增值—业态融合”的发展路径，为同类涉农企业推进农文旅融合、实现高质量发展提供了可借鉴的实践范式。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case presents the innovative transformation of Wangrui in Shunping County from a traditional agricultural model to an integrated agricultural-tourism enterprise. Initially reliant on the Peach Blossom Festival to draw visitors, the business faced a bottleneck due to the short blooming season and poor fruit sales. In response, as a national model worker, Zhang Guoqiao shifted focus from “selling peaches” to “selling experiences” and “brands,” establishing cooperatives, expanding e-commerce, partnering with experts for scientific farming, and launching deep-processed products like peach wine to extend the value chain. With geographical indication certification, Wangrui peaches gained market access through exhibitions and major supermarkets, transforming the farm into a regional benchmark with strong brand identity and technological capacity. More than just business success, Wangrui drove local development—empowering 17 villages and lifting 712 poor households out of poverty through its “peach orchard + tourism” model, earning Zhang the Hebei Provincial Poverty Alleviation Award. Now, at a critical juncture, Wangrui faces challenges such as market saturation and digital transformation. Can smart agriculture be the key to its next leap? This case illustrates how full-industry-chain integration and strategic innovation under rural revitalization policies offer a replicable path for similar enterprises aiming for sustainable, high-quality growth.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《管理学原理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业经营资源的概念与类型；资源基础观的核心思想；VRIO框架；企业家精神；差异化战略；一体化战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
